{"tid":978251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愛妻於樂富廣場殘廁上吊亡 丈夫搵到已太遲 (最猛係屌頸鬼)","createTime":"2019-01-11T18:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T18:03:45.000Z","uid":141892,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cd51ecec5e9712517dbd895cfb8973bdaf828b80","tid":978251,"uid":141892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T18:03:45.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=yYlPmL2gj%2Fdded%2FW4V25Iv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=3ce2d29f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】黃大仙樂富廣場A區，今日下午（9日）4時許，有職員發現一名婦人在UG層露天平台花園的傷殘人士洗手間內，以尼龍繩上吊，遂報警求助。消防及救護員接報趕至，將婦人解下，當時她已陷入昏迷，送院搶救後證實不治。警方在場調查，發現女死者姓劉（64歲），期間更發現她的丈夫正在附近尋找妻子，向他了解事件後，將他帶往醫院助查。<br />\n<br />\n警方經翻查商場「天眼」錄影片段後，初步相信事件沒有可疑，亦無檢獲遺書，案件列作「自殺」。消息稱，婦人有患病紀錄，曾向家人透露「好辛苦」，至今晨她外出後一直未有歸家，其丈夫大為擔心遂四出尋找。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/lQzOdUT0MkdMJapV5W5d0g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/512fca804bd145c24316b8da52fdcd03\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FlQzOdUT0MkdMJapV5W5d0g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F512fca804bd145c24316b8da52fdcd03&h=195713f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tnBd5Di9KDEMQW41xMb6LA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/78cb5f01fa95740eaf0f3f10ac9b3b25\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtnBd5Di9KDEMQW41xMb6LA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fm